is it a power of 2
Description

Given a number n, print YES if it is a power of 2 else print NO.


Input
1<=T<=10

1<=N<=100000000


Output
output a single integer, the answer to the question.


Sample Input 1

3
1
2
100
Sample Output 1

YES
YES
NO



SOLUTION--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

//Enter code here

import java.util.*;

public class Main{

  public static void main(String[] args){
    Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
    int tc=sc.nextInt();

    for(int i=0; i<tc; i++){
        int n=sc.nextInt();

    while(n%2==0)
    {

        n=n/2;
    }

    if(n==1){

        System.out.println("YES");

    }
    else{

       System.out.println("NO");

    }

    }
 }
}
